{{Infobox_NPC |name = Branden |image = Branden.png |personality = |time_active = Anytime |gender = Male |race = |age = 7th Term |location = [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] ([[Colony 11]]) }} '''Branden''' is a NPC in {{XC3}} who can be found in [[Colony 11]].
== Overview == Branden is a part of Colony 11's supply unit alongside [[Hexen]] under [[Easel]]. He is also the chef of Colony 11, and comparatively normal relative to the rest of the Colony, and has been shown to use diplomacy rather than violence to achieve his goals. He was a part of the elite Antares Squad of the [[Keves Castle]] guard in the past, along with [[Zoren]], Hexen, and [[Rattlejack]].
== Affinity == * [[Easel]] * [[Hexen]] * [[Rattlejack]] {{clr}}
